{"tid":2085753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"另一邊廂，歐盟跟隊制裁委國官員/人民，委國反擊驅逐歐盟大使","createTime":"2020-06-30T04:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T13:04:33.000Z","uid":14918,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"61c9237781a71578a3bf2f56f35894fee5f4f6fe","tid":2085753,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:22:16.000Z","msg":"2020-06-30 08:29<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歐盟制裁委內瑞拉官員　馬杜羅要求歐盟大使72小時內離開<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">歐盟宣布,制裁36名委內瑞拉公民,包括當地11名官員,禁止他們入境及凍結在歐洲的資產,理由是他們的行為違背國民議會,破壞委內瑞拉的民主、法治和人權。 </span><br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉總統馬杜羅其後要求歐盟駐首都加拉加斯大使,在72小時內離國。馬杜羅發表電視講話時,表示委內瑞拉受夠這種殖民主義式的干預與制裁。 美國在去年宣布承認反對派領袖瓜伊多為委內瑞拉合法領導人,馬杜羅政府與華府關係破裂後。馬杜羅在去年3月,曾要求美國駐當地大使在限時下離境。 (BC) #制裁<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E9%81%AD%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81-%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF72%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E9%9B%A2%E5%A2%83-015002881.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581-%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2585%25A7%25E7%2591%259E%25E6%258B%2589%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%25AD%2590%25E7%259B%259F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BD%25BF72%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25A2%2583-015002881.html&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=f35c295f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E9%81%AD%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81-%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF72%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E9%9B%A2%E5%A2%83-015002881.html</a>"},{"pid":"45317b0732cf51d155a9b9aa1a406e9a0a876082","tid":2085753,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d22e700dea9d2